{"tid":765641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民幣即期開市大跌２７１點子    人行連續9日暫停公開市場操作","createTime":"2018-08-03T03:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T08:07:10.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"0b793b747455f5723ef0050e0ce975119e836429","tid":765641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1410387_1_L_20180803092818.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1410387_1_L_20180803092818.jpg&h=1dbaaa95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n人民銀行今日不開展公開市場操作，是連續第9日暫停操作，今日並無逆回購到期。<br />\n<br />\n人行本周累計淨回籠2100億元人民幣。<br />\n<br />\n人民幣兌一美元中間價今報６﹒８３２２，至去年５月３１日以來最低，較上個交易日貶３８０點子。<br />\n<br />\n　　受隔夜美元大升影響，離岸人民幣上日（２日）暴瀉至６﹒８８水平收市，較前一個交易日跌５８４點子。人民幣兌一美元即期匯率（ＣＮＹ）今早跟隨向下，大幅低開２７１點子，報６﹒８５７１，上個交易日即期匯率收盤報６﹒８３００，開市後亦跌穿６﹒８６，低見６﹒８６０３，至逾１４個月低位，跌逾３００點子。"},{"pid":"eee196890400321a1aa6633a18037d36e39d80d4","tid":765641,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:11:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a01510ffb8248f872d4fb4d5eaf9607ccdc528b9","tid":765641,"uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:12:29.000Z","msg":"比美帝打到跪係度<br />\n<br />\n同美帝聯儲局比較, 支那人民銀行真係BB班咋<br />\n<br />\n返去飲奶啦！"},{"pid":"9d9b16c96d9390f39250768eb188f9b463bba9db","tid":765641,"uid":104699,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"快d到第一個站7.85"},{"pid":"f82be809e3dc2b87913047f6efc9a65b751cef58","tid":765641,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d12821868510380cceea48973595926e62a2ab0b","tid":765641,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:17:00.000Z","msg":"仲話國際化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d81503fae9a33140d20585bc7f7ed7942853c1f","tid":765641,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e59a74c77a571ce1144808552c1a223729a82ad5","tid":765641,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:47:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">人民幣匯價續弱 離岸人民幣兌美元一度跌穿6.89關口</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180803/s00002/e83d81f4fc9e817b4e3b70b09fb94020.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180803%2Fs00002%2Fe83d81f4fc9e817b4e3b70b09fb94020.jpg&h=63496640&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國聯儲局一如市場預期未有加息，美匯持續強勢，美匯指數最高見95.2水平。人民幣匯價續弱，離岸人民幣(CNH)兌美元一度跌穿6.89關口，低見6.8918，瀉0.15%，最新報6.8897，跌0.12%；在岸人民幣(CNH)兌美元亦連環跌破6.86及6.87大關，最弱見6.8766，屬去年5月底以來最低，最新報6.8701，跌0.4%。<br />\n<br />\n中國外匯交易中心公布，人民幣兌美元中間價大幅下調，今報6.8322，較昨日6.7942下調380點子或0.56%，屬去年5月底以來最弱。"},{"pid":"420f88801bee28706d3d144b92e12447baf18d79","tid":765641,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:53:36.000Z","msg":"暫停交易永遠唔會輸, 又贏多日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80c4c6fdea4ee120655f023d82cae9ee20e2259","tid":765641,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aa12f86da3a48b070f3c6aa389554d7765106c2","tid":765641,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T03:58:42.000Z","msg":"暫停操作<br />\n<br />\n即係點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"